# Language Policy

- **Communication**: You may address the agent in any language (e.g. Russian, English). The agent will understand and respond in the language you use.

- **Code and artifacts**: All of the following must be written in **English**:
  - Source code (identifiers, string literals used in the product, CLI messages)
  - Comments and docstrings in code
  - Documentation (README, docs, RULE files, commit messages)
  - User-facing text produced by the agent for this project

When adding or editing code, comments, or documentation, use English only. When replying to the user, you may use the language they used in their message.
